# Portfolio

A React application for displaying [a portfolio](https://www.benmyers.dev/).

[BenDMyers%20portfolio%20%F0%9F%91%A4%20A%20portfolio%20site,%20built%20with%](BenDMyers%20portfolio%20%F0%9F%91%A4%20A%20portfolio%20site,%20built%20with%)

## Setup

Installation:

```
git clone https://github.com/BenDMyers/portfolio.git
cd portfolio
yarn install
```

Usage:

```
npm start
```
